={
  "model": "mistral:7b",
  "prompt": "You are analyzing a BSE (Bombay Stock Exchange) corporate announcement.
Extract the following information and return ONLY a valid JSON object.
No explanation. No markdown. No extra text. Only JSON.

Required JSON format:
{
  "company_name": "exact company name from announcement",
  "event_type": "brief description of the event (max 5 words)",
  "sentiment": "Positive or Negative or Neutral",
  "impact_score": <integer 1-10>
}

If any field cannot be determined, use "Unknown" for strings and 5 for impact_score.

ANNOUNCEMENT TITLE: {{ $json.title }}
ANNOUNCEMENT CONTENT: {{ $json.content }}
",
  "stream": false,
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0,
    "num_predict": 100
  }
